---
description: Documentation specialist routing trigger
alwaysApply: false
globs:
  - "docs/**"
  - "docs/ai/**"
  - ".cursor/docs/**"
  - "**/README.md"
  - "**/*.md"
---

When a task updates or reorganizes documentation, the agent must consult `docs-agent` before finalization.

For non-trivial docs work, include:
- documented scope,
- consistency/interlinking checks,
- follow-up doc gaps.
